reviewText: This concert was very enjoyable and entertaining.

Love the concert and it is a new dvd showing 2014. CAUTION THIS IS EXACTLY THE SAME CONCERT THAT WAS RELEASED IN 2010. So if you a a Tanya Tucker fan like myself and have the 2010 concert DO NOT ORDER THE 2014 NEWLY RELASE OR YOU WILL FIND OUT AS I DID THAT YOU DUPLICATED THE SAME CONCERT FROM 2010
